{
  "stem": "15576.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 535.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And again, my family was intact.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they decided they don't have too many people in Korolowka.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[DRINKS] So they said, every-- liked they threw us out from Bilcze, that's how we throw out to Korolowka.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And again, we-- we lived with our distant family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The room was half this size.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It must-- Where did you go from-- Borshchiv.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "From Korolowka to Borshchiv.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not sure--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could only live where they assigned you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was not a ghetto surrounding, per se.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They gave you this street and this street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're not allowed to go here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You don't [INAUDIBLE] things like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No-- no-- no living facilities, no-- no toilets, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As I remember, it was-- it was a horrible thing, because everybody had to go, every night, empty those buckets.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And those buckets didn't have the-- you can-- you can imagine what it-- what it was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody liked to do it, but they had to do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they-- and then the picnic started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Borshchiv.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had one-- oh, yeah, before Borshchiv-- in Borshchiv, they were catching people to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Forced labor.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Catch-- no, they came home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them came home at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was just forced labor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a Jewish cop, Jewish policeman caught me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was with my brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my brother started crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Please, don't take him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have nobody at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Please.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He fell to-- to his feet and started kissing his boots.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Please, don't take him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He let me go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anyway, this is one episode.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They made Judenrein.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Judenrein meant-- no, that was not Judenrein yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We was there for a while yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Judenrein was about a couple of months later but the same thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
